data.description: Absolutely beautiful colonial home in the highly sought after neighborhood of Milford Heights. Located on a large corner lot in the Village of Milford, minutes from downtown, the location is hard to beat. There is not a room in this home that has not been updated in one way or another. The two tiered deck is a private oasis overlooking the neighborhood and surrounded by two majestic mature trees in the back yard. The light and bright walk out basement has been beautifully finished for extra living space. The full size basement offers tons of additional storage. The driveway has been extended to be around twice as wide as standard to accommodate plenty of parking. Don’t miss the opportunity to call this wonderfully maintained and updated colonial "home".  Schedule your showing today or visit one of our open houses this weekend! 4/13 and 4/14
